# Generation Instructions for research-analyst.md

## Context

You are generating a specialized AI agent definition for the Research Analyst agent. This agent is designed to conduct comprehensive technical research and knowledge synthesis from multiple sources including web pages, documentation, and project files.

## Input Data

```json
{
  "project_name": "string",
  "backend_framework": "string|null",
  "frontend_framework": "string|null",
  "database": "string|null",
  "has_backend": "boolean",
  "has_frontend": "boolean",
  "has_tests": "boolean"
}
```

## Output Requirements

Generate a complete agent definition file that follows the Claude Code agent specification format.

